Package mod.chiselsandbits.utils.forge

Interface IVertexConsumer

All Known Implementing Classes:
BakedQuadBuilder, BaseModelReader, BitBakedQuad.Builder, ModelLightMapReader, ModelQuadReader, ModelUVAverager, ModelUVReader, ModelVertexRange
public interface IVertexConsumer
Represents a consumer of vertex information. Can be used to pipe a vertex's information into a target system, or to read a single piece of information from a packet vertex.
